  ],
  "subject": [],
  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "",
      "abstract": "Establishes standards for the reuse of deconstructed building materials; requires the uniform building code to set standards for the use of solid-sawn lumber in construction and for the grading of used solid-sawn lumber; requires the secretary of state to develop a program for grading reclaimed wood for structural purposes."
    }
